 MAINTAINERS                            |   11 +++++++++++
 drivers/infiniband/Kconfig             |    2 ++
 drivers/infiniband/hw/Makefile         |    2 ++
 drivers/infiniband/hw/bnxt_re/Kconfig  |    9 +++++++++
 drivers/infiniband/hw/bnxt_re/Makefile |    6 ++++++
